# Visual Joke
The comic combines two meanings of "counting sheep" — the traditional insomnia remedy of mentally counting sheep — with a programming loop that increments a sheep counter while the person remains awake. The joke is that the person is literally executing code that counts sheep, yet they're still awake, suggesting the programming approach to sleep is as ineffective as the traditional method.
